---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 7rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-title">
        <h2>Tentang Demo Ini</h2>
        <p>Proyek mini yang menunjukkan keunggulan kecepatan Astro.js</p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-2" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>&#127919; Tujuan Proyek</h3>
          <p>
            Menunjukkan secara visual dan interaktif mengapa Astro.js lebih cepat
            dari framework JavaScript lainnya. Halaman ini sendiri adalah bukti &mdash;
            minim JavaScript, load instan.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>&#128296; Tech Stack</h3>
          <p>
            Astro v4 + Preact (untuk islands). Tidak ada React, Vue, atau
            framework lain. Node.js 20. Setiap halaman bisa di-build jadi HTML statis.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Fitur yang Didemokan</h3>

        <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem;">
          <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="min-width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(34,197,94,0.15); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem;">&#9889;</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Zero JS Default</strong>
              <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;">Halaman statis mengirim 0KB JavaScript ke browser</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="min-width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(124,58,237,0.15); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem;">&#127759;</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Islands Architecture</strong>
              <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;">Komponen interaktif terisolasi, sisa halaman tetap statis</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="min-width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(59,130,246,0.15); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem;">&#128202;</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Real-time Performance</strong>
              <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;">Ukur TTFB, DOM load, dan hydration langsung di browser</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div style="display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start;">
            <div style="min-width: 36px; height: 36px; background: rgba(234,179,8,0.15); border-radius: 8px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 1.1rem;">&#128640;</div>
            <div>
              <strong>Framework Comparison</strong>
              <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.9rem;">Perbandingan bundle size dan TTI vs Next.js, Remix, Nuxt, dll</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2.5rem;">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">&#8592; Kembali ke Home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
